e</i> <b>28</b> (1): 23–29. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2922719" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2922719" rel="nofollow">10.2307/2922719</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0002-9831%28195603%2928%3A1%3C23%3AFEODS%3E2.0.CO%3B2-W" class="external free" title="http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0002-9831%28195603%2928%3A1%3C23%3AFEODS%3E2.0.CO%3B2-W" rel="nofollow">http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0002-9831%28195603%2928%3A1%3C23%3AFEODS%3E2.0.CO%3B2-W</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-05-16</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Franklin%27s+essay+on+daylight+saving&amp;rft.jtitle=American+Literature&amp;rft.aulast=A.O.+Aldridge&amp;rft.au=A.O.+Aldridge&amp;rft.date=1956&amp;rft.volume=28&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=23%E2%80%9329&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.2307%2F2922719&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Flinks.jstor.org%2Fsici%3Fsici%3D0002-9831%2528195603%252928%253A1%253C23%253AFEODS%253E2.0.CO%253B2-W&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Satire"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
